  title: Bell Rings at 3:11 Tomorrow
  bodyText: 'Ding.

    This time, Room 217 calls the front desk.


    You answer.


    Static
    crackles for a moment before a woman calmly says:


    "Could you send up fresh
    towels?"


    There is no registered guest in Room 217.'
